<normalizedToken id="99F4BDDB08E1DE696A571B14304A2878" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
as long as wide. This species is distinguished by the elytral apex broadly rounded and entire, posterolateral margin continuously and smoothly carinate to striae 6 and not extended posteriad, declivital interstrial setae stout and scale-like, declivital interstriae minutely granulate, and declivital striae not impressed.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
